der%20G2%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20machine%20that%20automatically%20detects%20weeds%20and%20zaps%20them%20with%20a%20laser%20array.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMikesell%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20a%20neural%20network%20can%20be%20important%20%26quot%3Bto%20not%20just%20find%20where%20the%20weeds%20are%2C%20but%20to%20find%20the%20perfect%20place%20to%20kill%20the%20weed.%26quot%3B%20A%20neural%20network%20is%20a%20computational%20model%20inspired%20by%20how%20biological%20brains%20learn%20to%20process%20information%2C%20and%20is%20key%20to%20how%20modern%20AI%20systems%20function.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20agricultural%20industry%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fagtech-agriculture-industry-farming-methods-climate-change-labor-solutions-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20beginning%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20for%20farmers.%20That's%20good%20news%20for%20an%20industry%20struggling%20against%20foes%20like%20the%20climate%20crisis%20and%20shifts%20in%20trade.%20From%20complex%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fiot-technology-precision-agriculture-transforming-farming-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erobots%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-chatbots-like-chatgpt-work-explainer-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echatbots%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20farmers%20are%20testing%20out%20a%20range%20of%20tools%20to%20hone%20their%20processes%20and%20achieve%20goals%20once%20out%20of%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b2aeef5-3b4f-4c2c-a1e3-b0fd861703c7%5C%22%3EMachine%20learning%20takes%20the%20field%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMikesell's%20experience%20building%20autonomous%20vehicle%20infrastructure%20at%20Uber%20helped%20shape%20Carbon%20Robotics'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffermata-artificial-intelligence-technology-for-agriculture-plant-crop-health-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eapproach%20to%20agricultural%20AI%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20applying%20that%20same%20technology%20to%20the%20farming%20tools%20he's%20developing%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20computer%20vision%20systems%20used%20in%20autonomous%20vehicles%2C%20including%20cars%2C%20tractors%2C%20and%20other%20agricultural%20equipment%2C%20often%20rely%20on%20neural%20networks%20known%20as%20convolutional%20neural%20networks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECNNs%20are%20a%20form%20of%20neural%20network%20that%20can%20be%20trained%20to%20detect%20patterns%20in%20images.%20Carbon%20Robotics%20uploads%20images%20of%20weeds%20to%20its%20own%20database%2C%20where%20human%20labelers%20manually%20identify%20weeds%20and%20crops.%20These%20image-label%20pairs%20are%20then%20used%20to%20train%20a%20weed-finding%20CNN%20that%20can%20detect%20weeds%20using%20the%20LaserWeeder's%20onboard%20cameras%20and%20computer%20hardware%20in%20the%20machine%20itself%2C%20meaning%20no%20internet%20connection%20is%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Deere%2C%20the%20world's%20largest%20agricultural%20equipment%20company%2C%20also%20uses%20CNNs%20for%20multiple%20applications%2C%20including%20its%20autonomous%20tractors%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-artificial-intelligence-customer-experience-business-applications-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESee%20%26amp%3B%20Spray%20weed-detection%3C%2Fa%3E%20systems.%20At%20CES%202025%2C%20the%20company%20showed%20its%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deere.com%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fall-news%2Fautonomous-9RX%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecond-generation%20%26quot%3Bautonomy%20kit%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20can%20partially%20or%20fully%20automate%20common%20tasks%2C%20including%20tillage%20and%20weed%20removal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESarah%20Schinckel%2C%20the%20company's%20director%20of%20emerging%20technologies%2C%20said%20AI%20has%20already%20improved%20its%20agricultural%20equipment.%20In%202024%2C%20she%20said%2C%20John%20Deere's%20See%20%26amp%3B%20Spray%20system%20was%20used%20to%20spray%20over%201%20million%20acres%20of%20farmland.%20Because%20the%20machine%20only%20sprays%20plants%20identified%20as%20weeds%2C%20the%20system%20was%20able%20to%20weed%20this%20acreage%20using%208%20million%20gallons%20less%20herbicide%20than%20would%20typically%20be%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20think%20about%20that%20savings%2C%20as%20well%20as%20just%20overall%20productivity%20and%20sustainability%20improvements%20for%20them%2C%20that's%20just%20a%20win%20for%20them%20all%20around%2C%26quot%3B%20Schinckel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20also%20gives%20farmers%20more%20staffing%20flexibility.%20Semi-autonomous%20harvesting%20equipment%2C%20for%20example%2C%20gives%20the%20human%20operator%20AI%20assistance%20that%20can%20adjust%20the%20equipment%20more%20quickly%20than%20a%20typical%20operator%20can%20react.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20put%20somebody%20who%20maybe%20isn't%20an%20expert%20combine%20operator%20in%20a%20cab%2C%20and%20help%20them%20still%20achieve%20high%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Schinckel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2202e6bfc5-4456-4f9a-aee8-1a20c216c03d%5C%22%3EFarmers%20fire%20up%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20big%20agricultural%20companies%20are%20building%20tools%20with%20complex%20CNNs%20and%20other%20types%20of%20machine%20learning%2C%20some%20farmers%20are%20making%20use%20of%20more%20accessible%20AI%20tools.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fphillip-guthrie-38336a3%2F%3ForiginalSubdomain%3Dau%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPhillip%20Guthrie%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20the%20agriculture%20consulting%20firm%20Nine%20Creeks%20Consulting%2C%20often%20gives%20presentations%20on%20new%20technology%20in%20agriculture%2C%20including%20generative%20AI.%20He's%20already%20seeing%20farmers%20pick%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20planning%20and%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuthrie%20recalled%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20farmer%20who%20was%20having%20trouble%20with%20a%20data%20analytics%20platform%20he%20used%20to%20monitor%20and%20track%20weather%20at%20his%20farm.%20The%20analytics%20had%20never%20worked%20correctly%20for%20their%20operation%2C%20%26quot%3Bso%20he%20just%20took%20the%20raw%20weather%20data%2C%20threw%20it%20into%20ChatGPT%2C%20and%20started%20doing%20analytics.%26quot%3B%20The%20AI%20was%20able%20to%20handle%20the%20analytics%20tasks%20that%20prior%20software%20had%20failed%20to%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuthrie%20expects%20more%20farmers%20to%20start%20using%20generative%20AI%20tools%20in%20similarly%20specific%20and%20creative%20ways%2C%20perhaps%20bypassing%20the%20companies%20that%20make%20specialized%20agri-tech%20software%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c39ff796-9323-4906-8944-9f42ed3200ed%5C%22%3ETwo%20visions%20for%20generative%20AI%20in%20agriculture%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20techniques%20like%20CNNs%2C%20which%20are%20available%20today%20in%20autonomous%20agriculture%20equipment%2C%20represent%20a%20major%20leap%20in%20technology.%20Systems%20like%20the%20LaserWeeder%20G2%20and%20John%20Deere%20See%20%26amp%3B%20Spray%20were%20impossible%20to%20imagine%20a%20decade%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it's%20unclear%20how%20these%20task-specific%20examples%20of%20agricultural%20AI%20will%20fit%20with%20newer%20generative%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMikesell%20speculated%20that%20one%20solution%20could%20lie%20in%20integration.%20Carbon%20Robotics%2C%20like%20John%20Deere%2C%20doesn't%20use%20generative%20AI%20for%20its%20equipment%20and%20has%20no%20announced%20plans%20to%20do%20so.%20Still%2C%20he%20said%20that%20generative%20AI%20could%20become%20a%20%26quot%3Bplanning%20and%20human%20interface%26quot%3B%20used%20to%20operate%20equipment%20like%20the%20company's%20automated%20laser%20weeders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20say%20to%20the%20generative%20AI%20system%20that%20I%20want%20to%20clear%20this%202%2C000%20acres%2C%26quot%3B%20Mikesell%20said.%20%26quot%3BThen%2C%20it%20might%20come%20with%20a%20solution%20and%20say%2C%20why%20don't%20you%20deploy%20these%20laser%20weeders%20in%20this%20pattern%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuthrie%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20thinks%20that%20generative%20AI%20could%20drive%20a%20%26quot%3Bdemocratization%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20industry%20that%20larger%20companies%20may%20well%20miss%20out%20on.%20While%20the%20industry%20will%20always%20need%20heavy%20equipment%2C%20he%20said%2C%20farmers%20often%20express%20frustrations%20with%20the%20expensive%2C%20yet%20extremely%20specific%2C%20software%20available%20to%20the%20industry.%20%26quot%3BThe%20last%20thing%20they%20need%20is%20another%20tool%20that%20does%20one%20thing.%20What%20they%20want%20is%20a%20tool%20that%20does%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuthrie%20said%20with%20ever-improving%20generative%20AI%2C%20%26quot%3BYou'll%20have%20farmers%20who%20could%20build%20their%20own%20tools%2C%20conduct%20their%20own%20analytics%2C%20do%20their%20own%20automations%2C%20and%20focus%20on%20what%20they%20want%20for%20themselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%2C%20to%20me%2C%20changes%20the%20shape%20of%20agriculture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-tools-weed-control-efficiency-farming-agriculture-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750967701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c1e4cf748d8c055f455f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-tools-weed-control-efficiency-farming-agriculture-2025-6%